10
00:00:32,730 --> 00:00:35,920
Yeah, Connecticut. Not West Virginia.
对，康乃狄克州，不是西维吉尼亚

11
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:40,760
Maybe I'll drive you up there. I'd like to buy some tickets myself.
