- Sure. - I have an idea.
-当然 -我有个点子

16
00:00:56,380 --> 00:00:59,650
Why don't we all pitch in 50 bucks, we'll pool our money together..
我们可以各出资五十块 把钱集合起来

17
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:03,520
- and then if we win, we'll split it. - That's a great idea!
-然后如果我们中奖，我们就平分 -好主意！

18
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:06,390
No, thanks.
不用，谢了

19
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:09,390
- You don't wanna win the lottery? - Sure I do.
-你不想要中乐透吗？ -我当然想

20
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:11,590
I also want to be king of my own country..
我还想当国王咧

21
00:01:11,770 --> 00:01:14,530
and find out what happened to Amelia Earhart.
探索第一位飞越大西洋的女飞行员 是怎么了

22
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:18,300
- Still on Amelia Earhart? - The woman just vanished!
-还在想女飞行员吗？ -那女人就这样消失了！

23
00:01:20,010 --> 00:01:21,810
Seriously, you don't want in on this?
说真的，你真的不要加入吗？

24
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,910
No. Do you know what your odds are of winning the lottery?
不要，你们知道 中乐透的机率有多大吗？

25
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:28,710
I mean, you have a better chance of being struck by lightning 42 times.
比你被闪电打到四十二次的机率还小

26
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:32,080
But there's six of us, so we'd only have to get struck 7 times.
但是我们有六个人 所以我们只需要被打到七次

27
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,480
I like those odds!
我喜欢这种机率！

28
00:01:35,290 --> 00:01:39,190
Seriously, you guys, I can't believe you're gonna spend $250 on the lottery.
真的，你们，我不敢相信你们会 愿意花两百块钱在乐透上面

29
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:42,590
I mean, that's such a bunch of boo-hockey.
这实在太唬烂了吧？

30
00:01:45,930 --> 00:01:47,870
I'll ask.
我来问

31
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,090
"Boo-hockey"?
“唬烂”？

32
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:53,230
Oh, we think Emma's about to start talking..
我们认为艾犸已经快要开始说话了

33
00:01:53,410 --> 00:01:57,040
so we're trying to be careful about what words we use in front of her.
所以在她面前我们会小心用字

34
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:59,410
So get ready to hear a lot of boo-hockey..
所以准备好 你们会听到很多的“胡说”…

35
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:02,180
gosh darn it and brother pucker.
“讨厌”还有“惹人烦”等等

36
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:05,820
How do you know she's gonna start talking?
你怎么知道她要开始说话了呢？

37
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:09,850
When I talk to her, I almost feel like she understands what I'm saying.
当我跟她说话时，我几乎可以感觉到 她听得懂我在说什么

38
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:11,890
Kind of like Joey.
有点像乔伊

39
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:15,090
What's that now?
你说什么？

40
00:02:16,436 --> 00:02:18,427
The One With The Lottery

00:02:19,436 --> 00:02:20,427
rainystar压制iPod-MP4

41
00:03:06,650 --> 00:03:10,280
God, look at all these tickets. It's so exciting.
天啊，瞧瞧这全部的彩券 真是紧张刺激

42
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,490
I haven't won anything since sixth grade.
自从六年级后 我就没有赢过任何东西了

43
00:03:12,690 --> 00:03:14,990
Pie-eating contest?
吃派大赛呢？

44
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:20,320
You assume because I was heavy that's the only way I could win something?
因为我很胖，你就以为 那是我唯一能赢的比赛吗？？

45
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:23,520
No, I saw a picture of you covered in blueberries.
不，我看过你埋在蓝莓派里面的照片

46
00:03:23,730 --> 00:03:26,560
- That was a good day. - Yeah.
-那时候真快乐 -是啊

47
00:03:27,170 --> 00:03:31,130
- They're towing your car! - I'm parked in a garage on Morton.
-他们在拖你的车！ -我停在车库里面

48
00:03:31,970 --> 00:03:34,530
They're towing a car.
他们正在拖一辆车

49
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:38,440
And I am seeing spots.
我眼花了

50
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:41,310
Ross, you don't have Emma! Rachel, you don't have Emma!
罗斯，你没有在带艾犸！ 瑞秋，你也没有在带艾犸！

51
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,880
- Where's Emma? Who has Emma? - Joey, relax.
-艾犸呢？艾犸谁在带呢？ -乔伊，别紧张

52
00:03:44,050 --> 00:03:48,350
My mother picked her up two hours ago. You were there.
我妈两小时前来带走她了 你也在场啊

53
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:52,160
- I was? - Yes, and you talked to her.
-有吗？ -是的，而且你还跟她说话

54
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:55,650
- I did? - She dropped off a casserole.
-我有吗？ -她还带来了砂锅菜来

55
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:58,830
Oh, yeah, the casserole lady.
喔，对啊，那个砂锅女士

56
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:01,400
Did you come by to watch us win the big bucks?
你过来看我们中大奖的吗？

57
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:05,160
Yeah. And then I figured after you win, we can all go out to the balcony..
是啊，然后我想在你们中奖后 我们全部到阳台上…

58
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:09,780
and see a night rainbow with gremlins dancing on top of it.
看有小精灵在跳舞的夜间彩虹

60
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:13,240
Don't touch the phone! I'll get it!
别接电话！我来接！

61
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:16,340
- You think he washed his hands? - Hello?
-你觉得他有洗手吗？ -哈？

62
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:18,880
- Hey, Charlie, what do you know? - What's going on?
-嘿，查理，有什么消息？ -怎么回事？

63
00:04:19,090 --> 00:04:22,320
Chandler's supposed to find out if he's getting a job at his agency.
钱德想知道他有没有得到 公司内部的一个工作机会

64
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:24,890
But out of 15 interns, they're only hiring three.
但在十五名实习生中 他们只聘请三个人

65
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:26,890
- Tough odds. - Yeah.
-机率真小 -是啊

66
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:30,860
If only it were a sure thing like your 24-state lottery.
还真希望能像你们二十四州 联合彩券的机率一样高

68
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:35,700
Yeah, look who's coming around!
是啊，瞧瞧谁想通了！

69
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:39,600
Damn it. All right, call me when you know more.
该死，好啦，有更多消息再告诉我

70
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:43,810
- Did you get it? - One of the slots got filled.
-你有得到吗？ -一个名额已经被占了

71
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:48,750
- By you? - Sense the tone.
-被你吗？ -注意我的语气

72
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:53,580
- No, that kid Nate got it. - Oh, I hate that guy.
-不是，一个叫做奈特的小子 -喔，我讨厌那个人

73
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:56,990
I mean, come on, kid, pull up your pants!
我是说，真是的，小子 穿上裤子吧！

74
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:59,060
Well, there's two spots left, right?
还有两个名额不是吗？

75
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:01,890
Yeah. I mean, I want this so much. I wanna get one.
是啊，我真的好想要，我想要被录取

76
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:04,260
I want my friend Charlie to get one.
也希望我朋友查理被录取

77
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,530
Except I don't care about Charlie.
其实我不是很在乎查理

78
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,460
- Hey, you guys. - Hey!
-嘿，你们好 -嘿！

79
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:12,400
You are not gonna believe this. I just saw my psychic..
你们不会相信的 我刚刚去找过我的算命师

80
00:05:12,570 --> 00:05:16,440
and she said I was definitely gonna win the lottery tonight!
她说我今晚一定会中乐透！

81
00:05:17,810 --> 00:05:19,910
I thought we could use some extra luck..
我想要增加好运…

82
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:22,110
so I brought a wishbone home from work.
所以从餐厅带幸运骨头回来

83
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:28,780
A psychic and a wishbone? Guys, give someone else a chance.
算命师跟幸运骨头？ 拜托给别人一点机会吧

84
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:31,320
- All right, who wants to do it? - Can I?
-好了，谁要来做呢？ -我可以吗？

85
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:34,490
Vegetarians never get to do the wishbone.
素食者从来就没有机会玩幸运骨头

86
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:37,530
It's really not fair. Just because we don't eat the meat..
真是不公平，我们只是不吃肉

87
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:40,760
doesn't mean we don't like to play with the carcasses.
不代表我们不喜欢玩骨头

88
00:05:41,370 --> 00:05:43,100
All right. Rach?
好了，瑞秋呢？

89
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,670
I don't want that turkey smell all over my hands.
我不想要双手沾满火鸡的味道

90
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:49,430
I'll do it! It'll get the casserole stink off of mine.
我来，我要把砂锅菜的味道盖过去

91
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:54,510
- I hope I win. - Well, it doesn't really matter.
-希望我会赢 -嗯，没有关系

92
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,650
You're both wishing for the same thing.
你们的愿望是一样的

93
00:05:56,850 --> 00:06:01,620
I can't tell you what I'm wishing for, or else, you know, it won't come true.
我不能告诉你我许什么愿 要不然不会实现的

94
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:04,860
Right. But we know what you're wishing for.
对，但是我们都知道你许什么愿

95
00:06:05,090 --> 00:06:08,030
- I can't really say. - I understand.
-我不能说 -我了解

96
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:10,720
But you're wishing for what we think, aren't you?
但是你许的愿 跟我们想的一样，不是吗？

97
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:13,700
I'm not really comfortable with these questions!
我真的很不喜欢这些问题！

98
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,960
- Please! - Just do it!
-拜托！ -赶快做！

99
00:06:16,170 --> 00:06:18,140
Okay. One, two, three.
好的，一，二，三

100
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:20,210
I won! Hey!
我赢了！嘿！

101
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:23,500
You know what? I'm sure your wish is gonna come true.
你们知道吗？我确定 你们的愿望会成真

102
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:28,550
But, you guys, just in case, maybe a genie will come out if we rub this lamp.
但是，为了以防万一 我们来磨擦这个灯，或许精灵会出现

103
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:31,880
That thing gets hot!
那东西好烫！

104
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:33,710
Ross, just keep making your jokes.
罗斯，继续说你的笑话吧

105
00:06:33,890 --> 00:06:36,120
How are you gonna feel if we actually do win?
如果我们中了 你有什么感受？

106
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:39,490
- You're not gonna win. - I know the odds are against us..
-你们不会中的 -我知道机率很小

107
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:43,820
but somebody has to win, and it could be us. And then how you gonna feel?
但是总是有人会中，可能就是我们 然后你会觉得如何呢？

108
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:47,730
We're gonna be like, "Everybody, let's take our helicopters up to the Cape."
我们会说“大家开直升机去海角玩吧”

109
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:50,270
And you're gonna be all, like, "Oh, I can't, guys.
而你只能说喔，我不行…

110
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:53,670
I'll have to meet you up there. I gotta gas up the Hyundai."
我们到那边碰面好了 我先帮我的车子加满油

111
00:06:57,780 --> 00:07:01,840
Okay, I've heard myself on tape, and I sound nothing like that.
好了，我听过自己在录音带里的声音 我听起来根本不像那样

112
00:07:02,650 --> 00:07:05,210
I can see the headline now: "Lottery Winners' Friend..
我可以想像头条新闻是 彩券赢家的朋友…

113
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:07,790
Filled With Regret, Eats Own Arm."
充满懊悔，吃下自己的手臂

114
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,960
Why would I eat my own arm?
我为什么要吃自己的手臂？

115
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:13,750
Well, you wouldn't, but we own the paper. We can print whatever we want.
你当然不会，但是报纸是我们的 我们爱怎么写就怎么写

116
00:07:13,930 --> 00:07:16,560
You know what? I'm gonna throw in 50 bucks for you.
你知道吗？我帮你出五十块好了

117
00:07:17,230 --> 00:07:19,170
- Why? - Because I know that you think..
-为什么？ -因为我知道你认为…

118
00:07:19,330 --> 00:07:22,390
that the lottery is boo-hockey..
乐透是很唬烂的东西

119
00:07:22,770 --> 00:07:26,300
but we're all here, and we're gonna watch the numbers and have fun.
但是我们全都聚在一起 看开奖，会很好玩的

120
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:30,470
And you're my brother, and I want you to be a part of this.
而你是我哥哥，我希望你能参与

121
00:07:31,210 --> 00:07:34,910
You don't have to do that. I mean, I'll pay for myself.
你不需要这样做的，我可以自己出钱

122
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:38,950
But just the fact that you want me to have fun with you guys, that's so sweet.
但是你想要让我跟你们一起同乐 真的是太窝心了

123
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,750
Come here.
过来

124
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:44,260
Get a room.
去开个房间吧

125
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,260
So now that you're in, what are you gonna do if we win?
那既然你已经加入了 要是中奖，你要做什么事呢？

126
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:55,100
- I don't know. I'll probably just invest it. - Calm down.
-我不知道，或许投资吧 -对，要冷静

127
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:58,070
Seriously, that's your fantasy? To invest it?
正经点，你的梦想呢？投资？

128
00:07:58,270 --> 00:08:02,970
Oh, I'm sorry. Did I say, "invest it"? I meant, "Be cool and piss it all away."
喔，我很抱歉，我是说投资吗？ 我的意思是“快乐的全部花光光”

129
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:08,910
I know! We should pool all our money and buy the Knicks!
我知道了！我们该把全部的钱凑起来 买下尼克队！

130
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:11,120
I don't really care about the Knicks.
我不是很在乎尼克队

131
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:14,250
You will when I pick you as starting forward.
如果我选你当前锋，你就会了

132
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:18,650
You would do that? I never get picked!
你会那样做吗？我从没有被选上！

133
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:21,180
I'm not sure a sports team is the way to go.
我不确定球队会是正确的选择

134
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:24,730
You won't let me buy the Knicks? I can't believe you're taking this away.
你不让我买尼克队吗？ 我不敢相信你要打碎我的梦想

135
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:28,960
You're right, it has been your dream for over 15 seconds.
你说的对，这个梦想 已经有十五秒之久了

136
00:08:29,770 --> 00:08:33,230
How long until they announce the numbers, Mommy?
他们还有多久才会公布号码呢？妈咪

137
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:37,770
I'll take this one too. "Mommy"?
这个也让我来 什么“妈咪”啊？

138
00:08:38,450 --> 00:08:40,970
Oh, I've gotten into the habit of calling Rachel..
喔，我已经习惯叫瑞秋…

139
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:43,210
"Mommy" when we're around Emma.
“妈咪”，只要是艾犸在场

140
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:47,290
Which I now realize we are not.
我现在发现她并不在

141
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:51,830
I'm hoping that if she hears it enough, it'll be her first word.
我希望如果她听久了 这将成为她第一句会说的话

142
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:56,190
Although if we're gonna do that, we should probably call me "Daddy" too.
如果我们真的要这样做 你也应该叫我“爹地”才对

143
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:59,190
I like that, Daddy.
我喜欢，爹地

144
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:05,810
I was just talking about Rachel.
我只是在说瑞秋

145
00:09:06,010 --> 00:09:08,870
Is Daddy getting angry?
爹地生气了吗？

146
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:13,410
Is Daddy gonna spank me?
爹地要打我吗？

147
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:17,580
Well, that depends.
嗯，要看情况

148
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:20,520
Have you been a bad..? No, I can't.
你是不是坏…？ 不，我演不下去了

149
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:28,190
Hello? Hello? Hey, Charlie. Did anybody else hear?
哈？哈？嘿，查理 还有其他人知道吗？

150
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,720
What? Susan got it? How?
什么？苏珊拿到了？怎么会呢？

151
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:35,030
Oh, man, I would've slept with him!
喔，天啊，早知道我也跟他上床！

152
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,830
All right, bye.
好了，拜

153
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:41,030
Dude, I'm sorry. But hey, there's one spot left, right?
老兄，我很抱歉 但是，还有一个名额不是吗？

154
00:09:41,210 --> 00:09:43,900
- Well, Charlie's gonna get that. - Hey, don't say that.
-查理会得到的 -嘿，别那样说

155
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,740
You've got just as good a chance of getting that job.
你也有机会得到那工作的

156
00:09:46,950 --> 00:09:48,610
He is the boss' son.
他是老板的儿子

157
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:51,710
- Come on, lottery! - Yeah!
-好了，乐透！ -是啊！

158
00:09:51,890 --> 00:09:54,580
- It starts in, like,20 minutes. - Okay, here we go.
-再大概二十分钟就开奖了 -好了，我们来吧

159
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:58,120
We need to sort through the tickets quickly to see if we've won.
我们需要快点分配这些彩券来对奖

160
00:09:58,330 --> 00:10:01,020
So does anybody have any ideas how to organize this?
有人有什么主意要怎么安排吗？

161
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,360
Okay, how about this:
好的，看看这样如何

162
00:10:04,130 --> 00:10:06,190
We divide them into six groups of 40.
我们分成六组各四十张

163
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:09,390
The remaining 10 can be read by whoever finishes first.
剩下的十张就由先对完的人来对

164
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,370
- I have another idea. - I'm sorry, idea time is over.
-我还有一个主意 -很抱歉，提议时间已经过了

165
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,910
- Well, are all the tickets in the bowl? - Yeah.
-所有的彩券都在碗里了吗？ -是的

166
00:10:17,110 --> 00:10:20,570
- What about the ones on the nightstand? - There are no tickets there.
-那床头柜上面的那些呢？ -那边没有彩券

167
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:23,550
Yes, there are. I just saw them a few minutes ago.
是的，那边有 我几分钟前才看到

168
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:27,120
No, you didn't. You must be mistaken.
不对，没有，你看错了

169
00:10:27,290 --> 00:10:31,090
- There are 20 tickets on the nightstand. - Chandler, sense the tone.
-床头柜上有二十张彩券 -钱德，注意我的语气

170
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:36,960
Well, well, well. Look what Mommy found.
喔，喔，喔，瞧瞧妈咪找到了什么

171
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:41,300
Okay, fine. I bought 20 extra tickets for me and Chandler.
好啦，我帮自己跟钱德多买了二十张

172
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:45,230
The psychic also said that I would be betrayed.
算命的还说我会被朋友给背叛

173
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:49,810
I can't believe this. I thought we were all in this together.
我不敢相信，我以为我们是一起的

174
00:10:50,010 --> 00:10:53,340
- Hey, you just got in five minutes ago! - Three minutes ago!
-嘿，你五分钟前才加入的！ -是三分钟！

175
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:56,070
I don't know why that's important.
我不知道那有什么重要的

176
00:10:56,280 --> 00:11:00,410
I was with you the whole time. When did you even get those?
我一直都跟你在一起 你是什么时候买的？

177
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:05,120
When you were reading the dirty magazines without taking off the plastic.
当你在看未拆封的色情书刊的时候

178
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:07,190
I'll show you how.
我再分给你看

179
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:11,460
Okay. Well, Monica, suppose one of your special tickets wins?
好了，摩妮卡 假设你的彩券中奖了怎么办？

180
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:14,470
How are you gonna feel when you win and lose your friends?
你觉得中了彩券 失去了朋友又怎样？

181
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:18,470
Please. If I win the lottery, you guys are not gonna leave me.
拜托，如果我中奖了 你们才不会离开我

182
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:22,800
Someone gave me muffins last week, and I couldn't get rid of you for three days!
有人上星期给我一堆松饼 害我整整三天都被你们骚扰！

183
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:27,110
Chandler, would you just tell her what she did was wrong?
钱德，你可以告诉她这是不对的吗？

184
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:30,180
She's right. You shouldn't have bought tickets just for us.
她说的对，你不应该 帮我们两个另买彩券

185
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:32,010
Let me finish.
让我说完

186
00:11:32,190 --> 00:11:34,810
However, it doesn't look like I'm gonna get this job..
然而，看起来我好像得不到这份工作了

187
00:11:34,990 --> 00:11:39,320
so I can't afford to have principles. So screw you! The tickets are ours!
所以我不能太有原则 去你们的！彩券是我们的！

188
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:42,850
There's the man I married.
这才是我嫁的好男人

189
00:11:43,130 --> 00:11:45,390
All right. Believe me, if you win the lottery..
好了，相信我，如果你们中奖了

190
00:11:45,570 --> 00:11:47,560
it's the last you're gonna hear from us.
你们就跟我们不是朋友了

191
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:52,500
Fine. Don't be my friends. I'll buy new friends.
无所谓，不要当我的朋友就算了 我会买新朋友的

192
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:57,680
Yeah, and then I'll pay for their plastic surgery so they look just like you!
是的，我还会付钱让他们动整形手术 让他们看起来跟你们一模一样！

193
00:11:57,850 --> 00:12:00,470
You know what? I want my share of the tickets.
你知道吗？我要拿回我的份

194
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:03,140
I want my tickets too! And I'm buying the Knicks!
我也要拿回我的彩券！ 而且我要买下尼克队！

195
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,750
And Steffi Graf!
还有葛拉芙！

196
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:08,320
Cool. Then I want mine too! And if I win..
太好了，那我也要拿回我的！ 而且如果我中奖…

197
00:12:08,490 --> 00:12:11,650
I'm gonna put it all into a very low-yield bond!
我要拿全部的钱去买低利公债！

198
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:16,190
No. You guys, we gotta keep all the tickets together.
不行，我们必须要 把全部的彩券集合在一起

199
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,390
No. No, we should divide them up..
不，我们应该分一分

200
00:12:18,570 --> 00:12:21,000
and I should get extra because we used my car!
而且我应该多分点 因为是开我的车买的！

201
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,900
Hey! Hey! If anybody gets extra tickets, it should be me!
嘿！嘿！如果有人可以多拿一些 那个人应该是我！

202
00:12:24,070 --> 00:12:28,700
- This whole thing was my idea! - Yeah. Thanks for inventing the lottery!
-这整件事都是我想出来的！ -是啊，谢谢你发明乐透！

203
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:32,250
Just give them to me, and I'll split them up!
把彩券给我，我来分！

204
00:12:34,620 --> 00:12:36,670
Hey, hey!
嘿，嘿！

205
00:12:37,350 --> 00:12:40,380
God, I can't take it anymore! I'm putting an end to this!
天啊，我再也受不了了！ 我来结束这一切！

206
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:43,920
- Okay, if she jumps, I get her tickets! - Wait, no, no! Hey!
-如果她跳楼了，她的彩券就是我的！ -等等，不！嘿！

207
00:12:45,730 --> 00:12:48,720
If we're not doing this together, we're not doing it at all.
如果我们不要一起合资 那我们就什么都不要

208
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:51,230
- Say goodbye to your tickets. - No! No! No!
-跟你们的彩券说再见吧 -不！不！不！

209
00:12:51,430 --> 00:12:54,030
Do not come any closer!
不要再靠近过来了！

210
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:57,900
Can I come a little bit closer? Valuable things are getting squished.
我可以再靠近一点点吗？ 我的宝贝被压到了

211
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,770
Now, what's more important, your friends or money?
现在，什么比较重要？ 朋友还是钱？

212
00:13:01,010 --> 00:13:03,370
- Friends! - Money!
-朋友！ -钱！

213
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,240
Friends.
朋友

214
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,550
Hey, Monica, what about your extra tickets?
嘿，摩妮卡，那你其它的彩券呢？

215
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,550
They're all in there.
全都在里面了

216
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:17,820
- Even these five that I hid in my bra. - Monica!
-还有我内衣藏的这五张 -摩妮卡！

217
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:20,820
Okay. Good. You guys were so scared.
好的，很好，你们都吓坏了

218
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:23,830
There is no way I was gonna dump this..
我根本不可能会丢掉这些…

219
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:26,330
God! No!
天啊！不！

220
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:31,970
I think I broke your bowl.
我想我把你的碗摔破了

221
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:34,940
Go! Go! Go!
快、快、快！

222
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:51,320
What a beautiful night to be running around the street, looking for tickets.
到街上去找彩券 真是美好的夜晚啊

223
00:13:52,090 --> 00:13:54,290
And the wind sure made it fun.
而且被风一吹就更有趣了

224
00:13:55,130 --> 00:13:57,530
- Phoebe, we lost half of them. - So what?
-菲比，有一半不见了 -那又如何呢？

225
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:59,860
Monica, we have the winning ticket.
摩妮卡，我们还是会中奖的

226
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:03,500
My psychic said I was gonna win, remember?
算命师说我会中奖的，记得吗？

227
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:08,200
Weird your psychic didn't mention anything about the scary pigeon.
奇怪的是 算命师并没有算到可怕的鸽子

228
00:14:08,940 --> 00:14:12,540
As a matter of fact, she said that's how I'm going to die.
事实上她是有说过 我会那样死去

229
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:17,010
So excuse me for being a little skittish.
所以，原谅我有点被吓到

230
00:14:17,180 --> 00:14:19,350
There's two messages. This could be from work.
有两通留言，可能是工作的消息

231
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:23,220
- Oh, play them. - Okay. Here we go.
-喔，放来听听 -好了，来了

232
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:30,130
Hello. This is the pigeon from the balcony calling to apologize.
哈，我是阳台上的鸽子 打电话过来道歉的

233
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:36,040
I shouldn't have knocked the tickets out of the pretty lady's hand.
我不应该把彩券 从那个漂亮小姐手中弄翻

234
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:41,230
It was all my fault. Not hers. Bye.
这全是我的错，不关她的事，拜

235
00:14:47,050 --> 00:14:50,240
Well, I bet that was very hard for him to do.
嗯，我敢说要他这样道歉 一定很难

236
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:54,010
Hey, Chandler, it's Charlie.
嘿，钱德，我是查理

237
00:14:54,190 --> 00:14:56,050
This is it.
就是这个了

238
00:14:56,220 --> 00:15:00,390
Listen, it turns out I got the last spot.
听着，结果是我拿到最后的名额

239
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:03,390
I'm really sorry, man. It was a lot of fun working with you.
我很抱歉，老兄 很高兴跟你共事过

240
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:06,030
Give me a call if you want.
再打电话给我吧

241
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,930
Gosh, I ' m so sorry, honey.
天啊，我很难过，亲爱的

242
00:15:09,140 --> 00:15:10,660
Sorry, Chandler.
真替你难过，钱德

243
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:15,740
It is so unfair. It's like that time they promoted Saundra over me at work.
这真是不公平，这就像那次 他们升珊卓，而不是我一样

244
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,670
Was she related to Ralph Lauren?
她跟洛夫罗伦有亲戚关系吗？

245
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:21,540
No, she was just much better at her job than me.
没有，只是她工作能力比我强太多了

246
00:15:21,780 --> 00:15:24,150
You guys, the drawing's about to start.
你们大家，快要开奖了

247
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,750
We should call my mom's and say good night to Emma..
我们应该打电话给我妈 跟艾犸说晚安

248
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,950
- before she goes down. - Good idea.
-赶在她睡着以前 -好主意

249
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:32,250
Honey, you're being really strong about this.
亲爱的，面对这件事你真的很坚强

250
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:34,950
I know how badly you wanted that job.
我知道你很想要这份工作

251
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:37,960
Yeah, you know, I really thought I deserved it.
是啊，你知道的 我真的以为这是该给我的

252
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:43,570
But let's go win the lottery. I mean, we still have a 130 chances to win, right?
让我们来中乐透吧 我们还有一百三十个机会不是吗？

253
00:15:45,210 --> 00:15:47,610
Hundred and thirty-one.
一百三十一个

254
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:51,240
Yeah, good night, sweetheart. I love you.
是的，晚安甜心，我爱你

255
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:55,250
And remember, you're Daddy's little girl.
还有记住，你是爹地的小女孩

256
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:58,410
Phoebe's totally ruined that for me.
菲比完全毁了“爹地”

257
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,210
Hi, Mom. Put her back on.
嗨，妈，让艾犸听

258
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:05,380
Rach, they're announcing the numbers!
瑞秋，他们在开奖了！

259
00:16:06,130 --> 00:16:09,580
My God, I can already feel myself changing.
我的天啊，我可以感到自己在改变了

260
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:13,900
Here are your official Powerball numbers. We have 53.
这里是正式超级大乐透中奖号码 我们有五十三

261
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:16,590
- I've got that. - We have one too!
-我有 -我们也有一个！

262
00:16:16,770 --> 00:16:19,570
We are on the road, people!
我们快中奖了！

263
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:21,930
Come on!
快点！

264
00:16:22,140 --> 00:16:27,600
Mom, please, I know you love your new lips, but I can barely understand you.
妈，拜托，我知道你喜欢你的新嘴唇 但是我不太懂你在说什么

265
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:30,910
Would you please just let me say good night to my daughter?
你可以让我跟我女儿道晚安吗？

266
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,480
And here we go. The Powerball is seven.
然后接下来的号码是七

267
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:37,420
All right, check your numbers! Make me rich.
好了，你们快对号码！ 让我发财吧！

268
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:40,850
You guys, you're not gonna believe this.
你们大家，你们不会相信这个的

269
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:44,430
I was just saying good night to Emma, and she said her first words.
我刚刚在跟艾犸说晚安的时候 她说了第一句话

270
00:16:44,830 --> 00:16:46,730
- What? - Well, what did she say?
-什么？ -那她说了什么？

271
00:16:46,930 --> 00:16:49,770
She said, "Gleba"!
她说了“葛利巴”！

272
00:16:53,610 --> 00:16:55,840
Make me rich!
让我发财吧！

273
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:59,840
- Isn't that amazing? - Oh, yeah. No, no, no, that's great.
-是不是很惊人呢？ -是啊，真是太棒了

274
00:17:00,010 --> 00:17:01,740
Why aren't you more excited?
为什么你没有很兴奋呢？

275
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:06,180
Rach, gleba is not a word.
瑞秋，葛利巴不算一句话

276
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:10,610
- Well, of course it is. - Okay. What does it mean?
-它当然算 -好吧，那它是什么意思呢？

277
00:17:10,820 --> 00:17:13,850
Well, I don't know all the words.
嗯，我又不认识所有的字词

278
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:17,720
You know, I'm just glad I didn't miss my daughter's first word.
我只是很高兴我没有错过 我女儿说第一句话

279
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:22,270
- Yes you did! Gleba is a word! - Okay. Use it in a sentence.
-你就是错过了！葛利巴算！ -好的，那用它造句

280
00:17:22,470 --> 00:17:26,270
Okay. Emma just said, "Gleba."
好的，艾犸刚刚说了“葛利巴”

281
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:33,300
- It's not a word. - Okay, fine. I'm gonna look it up.
-那不算说话 -好的，我来查字典

282
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,000
Okay, great.
好的，太好了

283
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:38,310
While you're at it, she said another word the other day.
顺便查一下 有天她也说了另外一句…

284
00:17:38,490 --> 00:17:40,510
Why don't you look up:
你何不也查查看这个：

285
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:49,190
All right. Okay. Okay. Gleba. Gleba. Gleba. Gleba!
好了，葛利巴，葛利巴，葛利巴！

286
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:54,800
Here it is! "The fleshy, spore-bearing inner mass of a certain fungi."
找到了！“含孢子的丰厚菌种”

287
00:17:59,570 --> 00:18:03,100
She's gonna be a scientist.
她会成为科学家的

288
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:12,910
- Damn it. Anybody got anything? - No.
-该死的，有人有对到吗？ -没有

289
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:15,250
I'm still looking through mine.
我还在对我的

290
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:18,620
Just double-checking. No.
再对一次，没有

291
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:21,730
No. No.
没有，没有

292
00:18:26,570 --> 00:18:28,590
No!
没有！

293
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:34,600
Hello? Hold on.
哈？等一下

294
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:36,040
It's your boss.
是你老板

295
00:18:36,210 --> 00:18:38,770
The "I'm sorry I rejected you" phone call.
“很抱歉没用你”的电话来了

296
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:41,570
I'm not used to getting these from guys.
我还真不习惯男生打这种电话来

297
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:45,110
- Hey, Steve. - Chandler, hi.
-嘿，史提夫 -钱德，嗨

298
00:18:45,290 --> 00:18:48,220
I'm sure you've heard we filled the three positions.
我想你已经听说我们三个名额都满了

299
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:50,720
We felt that with your maturity and experience..
我们觉得以你的成熟度及经验

300
00:18:50,890 --> 00:18:53,360
you wouldn't be happy being someone's assistant.
你不会想要当助理的

301
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:56,120
I'd love to be somebody's assistant. Answering phones..
